Package game.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActorStatus
    Interface for actors that should be reporting their health and their weapons
    Aggressor
    Interface for Actors that have the ability to become aggressive
    Behaviour  
    Consumable
    Interface for items which it's uses are limited by consumable charges.
    EmberForm
    This interface is used to implement changes in LordOfCinder types
    IWindSlash
    Interface for managing wind slash action
    Resettable
    Interface for game objects that should be reset
    Soul
    A contract for soul-able instance (in other words, object/instance that has souls).
